Limit the Size of Your Query Results

To fast-track to meaningful insights, you can limit the size of query results in a lens. Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available with CRM Analytics, available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
Use CRM Analytics

To set the limit, click the gear icon and select Set Limit. Enter the size of the query result and click Apply.

If you edit your query in SAQL, also set the query limit in SAQL.

TIP: Use the query result limit along with a chartâ€™s auto-fit feature for a smoother scrolling experience.
